§II cssl-host-dmgm-specialists · 700-LOC · 8ad0780 ← merged
  PURPOSE : 4 cognitive-specialist roles · NOT generic-AGI
  ROLES   : DungeonMaster=0 · GameMaster=1 · Collaborator=2 · Coder=3
  KAN-BANDS : each-role gets-its-own-KAN-bias-band via observe_with_profile(...)
  API :
    pub trait Specialist :
      fn observe(&mut self, payload: &[u8])
      fn decide(&self, prompt_hash: u64) -> Decision
      fn role(&self) -> SpecialistRole
    pub enum Decision :
      ProposeAction { id: u32, params: Vec<u8> }
      Question { hash: u64 }
      Pass
    pub fn role_council(decisions: &[Decision]) -> Decision
      ↳ deterministic mediator · tag-rank + lex-encoding tiebreak
  TESTS : 15/15 · clippy clean -D warnings
  DEMO : Labyrinth/systems/dmgm_council_demo.csl · 17 fns · 1433-byte COFF

§II cssl-host-procgen-pipeline · 1006-LOC · 6c9a5bf ← merged
  PURPOSE : runtime-procgen spine ← Apocky's "engine = procgen NOT static scenes"
