§II cssl-host-substrate-intelligence (KAN-multiband) · b7b4329 ← merged
  PURPOSE : 5-band per-DisplayProfile KAN-bias accumulator · LIVE-LEARNING
  STATIC : KAN_BIAS_MULTIBAND : [[AtomicU32; 8]; 5] (5 bands × 8 axes)
  API (NEW) :
    pub fn observe_with_profile(digest: &[u8], profile_id: u8) -> i32
      ↳ profile_id ∈ {0..=4} matches Amoled/Oled/IpsLcd/VaLcd/HdrExt
    pub fn kan_bias_for_profile(pid: u8) -> [u32; 8]
  API (preserved) : observe(role,kind,seed,ev) routes to band-2 (IpsLcd neutral)
  DRIFT-RATE :
    Amoled/Oled : α=1/128 (2× faster · pitch-black panels · subtle bias-shift)
    IpsLcd/VaLcd/HdrExt : α=1/256 unchanged
  PERSISTENCE : format-version 0x01 → 0x02 · v1-back-compat-read
    v1 : 32 raw bytes → loaded into band-2 only
    v2 : 0x02 header + 5×8×u32 LE = 161 bytes
  TESTS : 25/25 (9 new + 16 pre-existing)

